{"tid":2490833,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［四月叫春］四月是你的謊言","createTime":"2021-04-16T01:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T18:01:35.000Z","uid":152712,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac8e73a750145be2d3d3b67f243a0be267ee552","tid":2490833,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVJrbYXqAGfDoAinAQFZ2nKeGDoHU3KhgVMB94aXnbNAR?filename=CaUaKbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaUaKbD.png&h=4a0490b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四月的春天<br />\n我和你第一次四目交接<br />\n我很期待這一天<br />\n因為我已經在你身邊徘徊了十年<br />\n早已深深愛著你&mdash;&mdash;有馬公生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNmTHmUYbQ9Z9ZnVpC5HGWVWWM9nNoyzYfupDHqEshBWd?filename=cidZCye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcidZCye.png&h=513a73a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是我和你的第一次合奏<br />\n亦是最後一次...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme7WTog1S5cc3J5hxA5fSr2bzjs2Nb4QNT6BWSpFh5VdW?filename=TMgo4du.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMgo4du.png&h=f7e483f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb8vpPadf2NCmLBMBX1QuJEwjH9NkxePRnKNQGizbLxzu?filename=jN4J4dv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjN4J4dv.png&h=18c25282&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRe2RvKx22YFjFLo4vUAg24MQ7GDVYYZZgqQ7kKsWFHAS?filename=Uh2fVka.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh2fVka.png&h=e975adb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我很享受星空下的時光<br />\n彷彿這個世界只有你和我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNhjqFNoK1kLanwUanyeJzDaDRkBht2zLUWkxFi24Ehej?filename=Zoj9ZNh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZoj9ZNh.png&h=deb62641&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcqfpGEXPx2uxh8M8wmYcqtnp6dTsToWBDeHmCQeqLE23?filename=ZCKmQTX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZCKmQTX.png&h=f8428d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你令我成為一道在黑暗中的光<br />\n沒有你就沒有我<br />\n因為是你點燃了我的生命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcq5p5rJiyVBCsujbHTKEhancmhT3wkCndUx2WLgfJJug?filename=bU46hzs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbU46hzs.png&h=03a764b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有我的四月又到了<br />\n我真的很想你<br />\n好想再和你相遇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWqE5b1pbuWaweuCspMJmvRnVJHiU5ZTKFaW62UKvkLUS?filename=rvRo4eN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvRo4eN.png&h=61a4f86c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6324d3dcd1749e27efaaf50c9c741e6693b896a","tid":2490833,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfe32d6b26ea5b100052156846601f22d735baa","tid":2490833,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6324d3dcd1749e27efaaf50c9c741e6693b896a","tid":2490833,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9446d35a8b9046aa09cd04617996bcd4ed1878af","tid":2490833,"uid":152712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6324d3dcd1749e27efaaf50c9c741e6693b896a",